<div class="title">Caffeine addiction warning</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Formaldehyde&Exact=1">Formaldehyde</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Formaldehyde. "Caffeine addiction warning: An Experience with Caffeine (exp7242)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 15, 2003. erowid.org/exp/7242</div>

